headline: PayPal Enhances Popular Online Credit Offering with New Physical Card for In-Store Use
summary: Today, PayPal announced that PayPal Credit can now be used everywhere with the introduction of a new physical card, issued by Synchrony (NYSE: SYF). This expands its popular digital PayPal Credit offering to use both online when checking out with PayPal and in-store and everywhere Mastercard® is accepted.

headline: Synchrony to Participate in the Morgan Stanley US Financials Conference
summary: Synchrony (NYSE: SYF) Chief Financial Officer, Brian J. Wenzel, will participate in a fireside chat at the Morgan Stanley US Financials Conference on Tuesday, June 10, 2025 at 8:15 a.m. (Eastern Time).
